WEBVTT

00:30.760 --> 00:34.530
It shall be the policy of this nation to regard any nuclear missile...

00:35.960 --> 00:39.100
...launched from Cuba against any nation in the western hemisphere...

00:40.240 --> 00:43.770
...as an attack by the Soviet Union on the United States.

00:47.040 --> 00:48.810
The cost of freedom is always high.

00:50.110 --> 00:53.580
No one can foresee precisely what course it will take.

00:54.380 --> 00:58.120
One path we shall never choose and that is the path of surrender.

01:03.630 --> 01:04.290
Are you ready for this?

01:04.730 --> 01:05.430
Let's find out.

01:24.610 --> 01:28.780
Listen to me very carefully, my friend. Killing will not bring you peace.

01:29.180 --> 01:30.390
Peace was never an option.

